<header>
  <h1>Connect Four Sample App</h1>
</header>

<div>
  
  <p>Connect Four (also known as Captain's Mistress, Four Up, Plot Four, Find Four, Fourplay, Four in a Row and Four in a Line) is a two-player game in which the players first choose a color and then take turns dropping colored discs from the top into a seven-column, six-row vertically suspended grid. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connect_Four" title="Connect Four Wiki">Wiki</a> </p>  

</div>

<table id = "board">
  <tr class = "0">
      <% (@board.cells). each do |cell| %>
        
        <td class = "<%= cell.y %>" > 
          <button 
            class = "cellButton buttons" 
            id = "<%= cell.x %>_<%= cell.y %>" 
            onclick = "play(<%= cell.x %>, <%= cell.y %>)">
              <%= cell.x %> <%= cell.y %>
              <input type = "hidden" 
                id = "played_<%= cell.x %>_<%= cell.y %>" 
                value = "<%= cell.played %>" /> 
          </button>
        </td>

        <% if cell.y == (@board.cols - 1)  %>
          </tr>
          <% if cell.x != (@board.rows - 1)  %>
            <tr class = "<%= cell.x + 1 %>">
          <% end %>
        <% end %>

      <% end %>

</table>

<input type="hidden" id="clicks" value="0"/>